dblp.social.importer
Class DblpImporterHandler

java.lang.Object
  org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      dblp.social.importer.DblpImporterHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler
public class DblpImporterHandler
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler

This class defines the handler that allows the SAX XML Reader to parse, model and store the dblp data using Hibernate.
